high_descs: Turn right to walk to the dining room and reach the right side of the diningtable.
Pick up the potato from the bowl on the table.
Turn around to walk to the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around and walk left to exit the room and face the coffeetable on the right.
Put the potato on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated Potato on the CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Go straight and turn right to the dining room, then move to the corner of the room facing the diningtable.
Pick a potato from the table and turn around.
Place that vegetable in the microwave by opening it, then close it.
Heat that potato in the microwave and take it out by opening the oven, then close it.
Turn right and go back to the living room heading towards the coffeetable in the center of the living room.
Now put the potato on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Place the potato on the coffee table by heating it in the microwave oven.
